requerimientos 

kafka-python==2.0.2
pandas==2.0.3
flask==2.3.3
flask-cors==4.0.0
pymongo==4.6.0
numpy==1.24.3
dnspython==2.4.2  # Requerido para conexiones mongodb+srv (MongoDB Atlas)

